      Format="Bead of Healing 1/day -- Wearer can cast his choice of cure serious wounds, remove blindness/deafness, or remove disease.  Bead of Karma 1/ day -- Wearer casts his spells at +4 caster level. Effect lasts 10 minutes.  Bead of Summons 1 time only -- Summons a powerful creature of appropriate alignment from the Outer Planes (an angel, devil, etc.) to aid the wearer for one day. (If the wearer uses the bead of summons to summon a deity's emissary frivolously, the deity takes that character's items and places a geas/quest upon him as punishment in the very least.)  Bead of Wind Walk 1/day -- Wearer can cast Wind Walk",
